  <excursions><![CDATA[<p><strong>Book locally </strong></p>
<p>Explore the local area independently with these recommended trips. </p>
<p>Prices are approximate only.</p>
<p><strong>Norway in a Nutshell</strong> £119, full day, daily</p>
<p>A fabulous circuit by train and bus from Voss including the famous Flåm mountain railway and scenic Aurlandfjord boat cruise. Public bus from Lofthus to Voss extra (pay locally)</p>
<p><strong>Eidfjord and Vøringfossen incl. Hardangervidda Nature Centre</strong> £69, daily</p>
<p>A roundtrip starting by boat to Eidfjord and then bus to the Vøringfossen waterfalls and including a visit to the Hardangervidda Nature Centre. Reduced prices available for 67yrs+. </p>
<p><strong>Idyllic Ulvik by boat</strong>, £32, daily </p>
<p>Take the express boat to the end of the Hardangerfjord and the quaint and peaceful village of Ulvik. Reduced prices available for 67yrs+. </p>]]></excursions>
